                    </div>

                    <div class="consultation-note">
                        <p><strong>Not sure which session length?</strong> Check what we discussed in your consultation. Small pieces = 2-3 hours, Medium = 4-6 hours, Full day = 6-7 hours.</p>
                    </div>
